overview: On this edition of Hitting the Highspots, Naylor is joined by Mr. Athletic Jeff Cobb. Jeff tells his very unique story of growing up in Hawaii, wrestling in the Olympics for Guam, and getting into professional wrestling.  This Matanza of a man, has always loved pro wrestling and has been tearing it up for the last few years.  So sit back, take a tour of the islands, and get to know Jeff Cobb.
title: Hitting The Highspots - Jeff Cobb
